1
00:01:29,539 --> 00:01:33,170
[Cage of Shadows]

2
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:36,050
[Episode 11]

3
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,240
Ms. Kou,

4
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:39,000
I advise you to sign

5
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:41,410
and put your fingerprint
on Xie Quan's confession of guilt

6
00:01:41,410 --> 00:01:43,800
-sooner rather than later.
-Mr. Xie is modest and courteous,

7
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:45,060
of upright character.

8
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:46,360
He would never do

9
00:01:46,360 --> 00:01:48,000
such heinous things.

10
00:01:48,520 --> 00:01:49,320
Hmph.

11
00:01:49,500 --> 00:01:51,360
Such an unbreakable bond of love.

12
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:52,120
Guards,

13
00:01:52,240 --> 00:01:53,120
beat her!

14
00:01:58,289 --> 00:02:00,120
[Xie Mansion]

15
00:02:00,440 --> 00:02:03,940
[Xie Mansion]

16
00:02:01,420 --> 00:02:02,590
Half a year later,

17
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:05,160
the matter with Prince Xu came to an end.

18
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:07,080
Ms. Kou was released,

19
00:02:07,780 --> 00:02:09,900
but having endured brutal torture,

20
00:02:07,860 --> 00:02:09,270
[Xie Mansion]

21
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:11,610
she was covered in scars

22
00:02:12,010 --> 00:02:13,660
[Xie Mansion]

23
00:02:12,130 --> 00:02:12,960
and left with a broken body.

24
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:13,920
Hey, what are you doing?

25
00:02:13,920 --> 00:02:14,880
Get out.

26
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:17,530
Where did you come from, you beggar?

27
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:18,950
Do you know where this is?

28
00:02:18,950 --> 00:02:19,920
How dare you barge in here?

29
00:02:19,920 --> 00:02:22,870
I'm looking for Mr. Xie Quan.

30
00:02:22,900 --> 00:02:25,560
Our Mr. Xie has married into
the Princess Mansion.

31
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:26,380
He doesn't live here.

32
00:02:26,380 --> 00:02:28,050
You stinking beggar,

33
00:02:28,079 --> 00:02:29,480
why don't you take a look at yourself
in the mirror?

34
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:31,760
Do you think the Prince Consort is
someone you can just ask to meet?

35
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:33,160
When did he marry into
the Princess Mansion?

36
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:33,960
Get out of here right now!

37
00:02:33,250 --> 00:02:36,829
[Xie Mansion]

38
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:36,210
What are you arguing about?

39
00:02:36,230 --> 00:02:37,810
What's the noise?

40
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:43,120
The hairpin.

41
00:02:43,640 --> 00:02:45,200
This is my hairpin.

42
00:02:45,200 --> 00:02:47,760
This was a reward from our master.

43
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:49,360
What's it to you?

44
00:02:50,970 --> 00:02:51,910
Ru Yue.

45
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,400
You are Ru Yue.

46
00:02:53,480 --> 00:02:54,640
I am Ms. Kou.

47
00:02:54,640 --> 00:02:56,079
I'm not Ru Yue.

48
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:56,920
You got the wrong person.

49
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:57,850
I am Ms. Kou.

50
00:02:57,870 --> 00:02:58,350
Go, go, go, go!

51
00:02:58,350 --> 00:02:58,880
-Hurry up!
-Ru Yue.

52
00:02:58,880 --> 00:03:00,480
Go, go, go, go!

53
00:03:01,610 --> 00:03:06,860
[Xie Mansion]

54
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,910
[Xie Mansion]

55
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:12,650
To extricate himself from the matter
involving Prince Xu,

56
00:03:12,650 --> 00:03:15,100
Xie Quan ultimately chose to marry into
the Princess Mansion.

57
00:03:12,970 --> 00:03:14,680
[Xie Mansion]

58
00:03:15,940 --> 00:03:18,040
And Ms. Kou's savings

59
00:03:18,070 --> 00:03:20,270
were swindled away by her own maid.

60
00:03:21,829 --> 00:03:23,950
Poor thing,
during those six months in prison,

61
00:03:23,720 --> 00:03:31,220
[Xie Mansion]

62
00:03:24,600 --> 00:03:28,079
she had been foolishly clinging to
those so-called promises.

63
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,840
Don't you think

64
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:34,000
that this Ms. Kou

65
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:37,570
is the most foolish woman in the world?

66
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:40,400
Then I want to know;

67
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:42,520
what happened to that heartless man

68
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:43,810
and that ungrateful maid

69
00:03:43,810 --> 00:03:44,810
in the end?

70
00:03:44,880 --> 00:03:45,680
Oh.

71
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:51,720
One year, on the fifteenth day

72
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:55,100
of the first lunar month,

73
00:03:55,480 --> 00:03:57,280
people found the severed arms,

74
00:03:57,920 --> 00:03:59,450
legs, and heads

75
00:04:00,150 --> 00:04:02,100
of the Prince Consort Xie

76
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:03,440
and Ru Yue

77
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:06,160
scattered all over the city.

78
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:16,589
After hearing my story,

79
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:20,160
do you still believe in promises?

80
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:23,780
Sweet words come from no loyal lips.

81
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:26,620
The fickle world abounds
with smooth‑talkers.

82
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:28,860
It's getting late.

83
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:29,880
I advise you

84
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:31,360
to take this gold.

85
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:35,960
I will have someone
escort you safely to the fourth level.

86
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:40,320
You've finished your story.

87
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:41,840
I have a story too.

88
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,340
This ring,

89
00:04:47,020 --> 00:04:48,460
do you remember it?

90
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:50,860
This is the guiding ring of Lingya Tower.

91
00:04:51,070 --> 00:04:52,430
Where did you get it?

92
00:04:53,140 --> 00:04:54,520
Ten years ago,

93
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:58,240
Lingya Tower sent an assassin
who killed my father.

94
00:04:58,260 --> 00:04:59,980
My mother was also poisoned
with a strange toxin,

95
00:04:59,980 --> 00:05:01,160
and has been unconscious ever since.

96
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:03,000
And this ring

97
00:05:03,280 --> 00:05:05,800
was left behind by the killer then.

98
00:05:05,820 --> 00:05:07,420
I fought my way up the Tower

99
00:05:07,520 --> 00:05:09,800
and learned
that the killer was voice-keeper Taiyin.

100
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:10,660
And she

101
00:05:11,320 --> 00:05:13,120
is right here on the third level.

102
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:14,920
Are you saying

103
00:05:15,290 --> 00:05:16,250
that I am

104
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:18,560
the one who killed your father?

105
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,360
That's right.

106
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:21,600
I should kill you
with my own hands right now

107
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:22,690
to avenge them,

108
00:05:23,200 --> 00:05:25,130
but my Master repeatedly warned me

109
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:27,080
not to act recklessly.

110
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,840
So on some matters,

111
00:05:31,080 --> 00:05:33,440
I decided to ask you face to face.

112
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:37,440
Your Master,

113
00:05:37,760 --> 00:05:38,720
Zhuang Wujiu?

114
00:05:42,460 --> 00:05:43,920
What else did she tell you?

115
00:05:45,159 --> 00:05:46,680
Are you suspecting

116
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:48,360
that the voice-keeper on the third level

117
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:50,420
is the one who murdered your parents?

118
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:53,020
That man with a hairpin

119
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:54,640
is so ruthless.

120
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,280
How could he not be

121
00:05:56,280 --> 00:05:57,400
the voice-keeper Taiyin.

122
00:05:57,400 --> 00:05:58,200
Yes

123
00:05:59,960 --> 00:06:00,760
and no.

124
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,360
What do you mean?

125
00:06:03,320 --> 00:06:04,780
Let me take you somewhere.

126
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:07,680
Zan Hua

127
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:09,480
is not the voice-keeper.

128
00:06:22,820 --> 00:06:24,010
I've been here before.

129
00:06:24,010 --> 00:06:25,240
Isn't this where female prisoners

130
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,400
are enslaved to mint coins?

131
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:27,200
Exactly.

132
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:28,720
Look closely.

133
00:06:35,260 --> 00:06:36,500
No!

134
00:06:36,760 --> 00:06:37,840
Ah!

135
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:40,720
Hey!

136
00:06:40,810 --> 00:06:44,070
Isn't that the female prisoner
who played the Golden Cave?

137
00:06:44,280 --> 00:06:45,540
She's still alive.

138
00:06:49,520 --> 00:06:51,080
By order of Tower Master,

139
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:52,600
the voice-keeper mints new coins here.

140
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:54,850
Smelting gold requires excavating caves.

141
00:06:54,850 --> 00:06:56,190
Later she discovered

142
00:06:56,220 --> 00:06:58,320
that by using the complex
and varied cave structures,

143
00:06:58,320 --> 00:07:00,200
she could hide female prisoners in them,

144
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:01,160
making them hard to find,

145
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:03,640
so she started
helping these female prisoners

146
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:04,520
fake their deaths

147
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:05,820
to deceive everyone.

148
00:07:07,180 --> 00:07:09,480
Even if she has found her conscience now,

149
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:10,570
it doesn't prove

150
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:12,520
that she isn't the one
who murdered my parents.

151
00:07:12,520 --> 00:07:14,060
On the entire third level,

152
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:16,000
apart from the voice-keeper,

153
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:16,920
there is no one else

154
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,000
with that ability.

155
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:25,280
She even told you all this.

156
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,480
I know

157
00:07:29,950 --> 00:07:31,510
you've saved many people.

158
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:33,280
But when facing an enemy,

159
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:35,370
I will never show mercy.

160
00:07:35,400 --> 00:07:36,530
The answer you want,

161
00:07:37,280 --> 00:07:38,760
I can tell you right now.

162
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:42,850
I am not the voice-keeper Taiyin,

163
00:07:43,159 --> 00:07:46,440
and this ring is not mine.

164
00:07:47,880 --> 00:07:50,570
All guiding rings
for voice-keepers of Lingya Tower

165
00:07:50,570 --> 00:07:53,210
are sized for the left ring finger.

166
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,680
The size of this ring...

167
00:07:58,880 --> 00:07:59,960
See?

168
00:08:00,830 --> 00:08:03,000
It shows the owner's finger

169
00:08:03,260 --> 00:08:04,720
is much thinner than mine.

170
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,160
I apologize for my offense just now.

171
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:17,520
Please forgive me,

172
00:08:17,650 --> 00:08:18,330
Ms. Kou.

173
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:21,840
Zan,

174
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:23,000
put the sword down.

175
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:23,760
Wan,

176
00:08:24,330 --> 00:08:27,460
it would be one thing
if she were just an ordinary person,

177
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:28,880
but she's with Zhuang Wujiu.

178
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:30,320
I can't let her leave.

179
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:30,920
Zan,

180
00:08:31,080 --> 00:08:32,539
let her go.

181
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:34,820
Are you not even going to listen to me?

182
00:08:36,799 --> 00:08:38,559
You previously hid the truth
from Tower Master,

183
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:40,620
mixing impurities into the coinage,

184
00:08:40,679 --> 00:08:42,240
secretly transferring the remaining gold

185
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:44,000
to Zhuang Wujiu for transport.

186
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,280
That alone is a capital offense!

187
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:47,880
If it weren't for her
repeatedly bewitching you,

188
00:08:47,880 --> 00:08:50,540
how could you have done
such a rebellious thing?

189
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:51,720
Listen to me.

190
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,360
Let's capture this person

191
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:54,840
and report to Tower Master.

192
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:56,700
Maybe we can make amends for our crimes.

193
00:08:56,700 --> 00:08:57,610
Zan

194
00:08:57,760 --> 00:08:58,760
Zan, don't.

195
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,280
Kou Wan.

196
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:05,200
Lingya Tower has always been brutal
and ruthless.

197
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:06,440
Having been here for so many years,

198
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:07,900
how could we not know that?

199
00:09:08,400 --> 00:09:09,680
Even if you grab her and run,

200
00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:11,400
I still can't escape death.

201
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:13,280
Releasing the female prisoners

202
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:16,450
is an act of redemption
I truly wanted to do.

203
00:09:16,520 --> 00:09:18,650
It has nothing to do with Zhuang Wujiu.

204
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:21,320
Even if I die,

205
00:09:21,370 --> 00:09:23,540
I could never be a treacherous person.

206
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:44,600
Why did Master summon me

207
00:09:44,770 --> 00:09:45,850
overnight?

208
00:09:47,220 --> 00:09:49,080
There are two chests of gold here.

209
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:51,360
This chest is the one I sealed previously.

210
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:53,960
And this one is what you delivered
two days ago.

211
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:55,600
Forgive my ignorance, Master.

212
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:57,460
I do not understand what you mean.

213
00:09:58,490 --> 00:10:00,260
Then watch closely.

214
00:10:24,760 --> 00:10:26,040
I failed in my duty of supervision.

215
00:10:26,040 --> 00:10:27,770
I deserve ten thousand deaths.

216
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:39,170
What happened?

217
00:10:39,170 --> 00:10:41,480
The adulteration of the gold coins
has been discovered.

218
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:43,040
Tower Master is coming to punish us.

219
00:10:43,040 --> 00:10:45,610
I've arranged everything else.

220
00:10:45,640 --> 00:10:46,900
Leave with me quickly.

221
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:48,520
I can't leave.

222
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:49,840
If I leave,

223
00:10:49,920 --> 00:10:51,280
Tower Master will blame

224
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:53,080
everything on Zan.

225
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:53,530
What's more,

226
00:10:53,530 --> 00:10:55,440
the female prisoners we painstakingly hid

227
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:56,650
will certainly die.

228
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:58,320
I will do my best to mediate

229
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:59,080
and keep everyone safe.

230
00:10:59,080 --> 00:11:00,340
But if you don't leave,

231
00:11:00,400 --> 00:11:01,620
you will die.

232
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:07,000
Sorry, Zhuang Wujiu.

233
00:11:08,280 --> 00:11:10,740
This needle will put you
to sleep for a while.

234
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:14,760
Zhuang Wujiu.

235
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:17,320
There is absolutely no way
I can escape unscathed this time.

236
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:18,440
Only my death

237
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:20,520
can ensure all your safety.

238
00:11:20,520 --> 00:11:22,110
You and I still have unfinished business.

239
00:11:22,110 --> 00:11:22,840
You can't...

240
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:23,640
Zhuang Wujiu.

241
00:11:23,880 --> 00:11:24,540
Promise me.

242
00:11:24,640 --> 00:11:26,400
Those gold coins we hid away,

243
00:11:26,400 --> 00:11:27,470
you must guard them well.

244
00:11:27,470 --> 00:11:29,790
And if someday those female prisoners

245
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:32,520
manage to leave Lingya Tower alive,

246
00:11:33,160 --> 00:11:34,450
I leave them in your care.

